{"tid":2396281,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國又開始印銀紙","createTime":"2021-02-05T12:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T15:03:35.000Z","uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5326f9c238938a9411a978206f593f6bc62aeacb","tid":2396281,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">美国又开始印银纸<br />\n<br />\nFolks often wonder why Japan didn't have inflation over the past 20 years despite their central bank balance sheet going vertical.<br />\n<br />\nIt's because their broad money supply grew very slowly.<br />\n<br />\nBase money going vertical, and broad money going vertical, are two very different things.<br />\n<br />\n- Lyn Alden 2/4/21<br />\n<br />\nVery important distinction<br />\n<br />\nInteresting to note broad USD starting to head vertical in this chart<br />\n<br />\n- Joseph Brown 2/4/21</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NDPPAO7qZpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNDPPAO7qZpE&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=6a6c1104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NDPPAO7qZpE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSxamdn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSxamdn.png&h=26989183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54c8d4140ac2f24db3609ea0a43ac4b9a21be5ff","tid":2396281,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-05/senate-adopts-blueprint-for-major-stimulus-as-harris-breaks-tie\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2021-02-05%2Fsenate-adopts-blueprint-for-major-stimulus-as-harris-breaks-tie&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=566e502e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-05/senate-adopts-blueprint-for